code: public Exchange aggregate(Exchange oldExchange, Exchange newExchange) {     // the first time we only have the new exchange     if (oldExchange == null) {         return newExchange.     }     if (oldExchange.getIn().getBody(int.class) < newExchange.getIn().getBody(int.class)) {         return oldExchange.     } else {         return newExchange.     } }
